     C                     PARM           WKOSN   2        ﾃcﾆ] hﾎﾞ]
     C                     PARM           PZKMS2  50       ud ﾉ f]ﾌﾞ] ubﾇc
     C                     PARM           US               ﾏｰﾅﾞｰxb
